    "rich_text_8Va99j": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_mje4qq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>I believe there are some basic biomechanics to how the skeleton and skull work, which result in it collapsing over time.<br/><br/>Particularly if you did orthodontics, extractions, or grind your teeth because those things flatten your 'curve of spee', which is the natural curve of how your upper & lower teeth make contact.<br/><br/>And Reviv essentially aimes to reverse that collapse, thereby reinflating the skull and skeleton back to their healthy state.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
